1
00:00:33,040 --> 00:00:34,535
What is Ran even doing?

2
00:00:35,741 --> 00:00:37,046
Does she have any idea what he’s doing?

3
00:00:37,569 --> 00:00:39,513
Yeah, I’m totally shocked too.

4
00:00:39,532 --> 00:00:41,661
I don’t know what Chat is thinking.

5
00:00:42,141 --> 00:00:44,566
But  you know this is wrong.

6
00:00:44,584 --> 00:00:46,178
I know.

7
00:00:46,400 --> 00:00:47,520
You’re so weak.

8
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,203
What is wrong with you guys?

9
00:03:13,270 --> 00:03:14,030
Is something up?

10
00:03:15,290 --> 00:03:19,618
What were you and Ranya doing in the restroom yesterday?

11
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:25,138
I... I didn’t do anything.

12
00:03:28,110 --> 00:03:30,203
Are you guys crazy?

13
00:03:30,227 --> 00:03:31,987
We heard everything.

14
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:35,753
Just think about it, if it hadn't been us who heard you.

15
00:03:36,250 --> 00:03:40,196
what you did could have absolutely ruined your lives.

16
00:03:40,209 --> 00:03:40,953
Do you even realize that?

17
00:03:42,950 --> 00:03:44,430
P'Tina, you heard us?

18
00:03:46,220 --> 00:03:47,433
I heard it too.

19
00:03:49,538 --> 00:03:51,530
Stop this right now, Ran.

20
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:54,061
This is seriously messed up,it’s totally immoral.

21
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,326
Hey!

22
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:03,335
And you guys are still standing there smiling?

23
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:05,212
This is a massive deal!

24
00:04:05,230 --> 00:04:07,427
Think about the stocks, the news... What the hell are you guys even doing?!

25
00:04:07,452 --> 00:04:10,098
I’m sorry.

26
00:04:10,790 --> 00:04:13,009
I’m sorry I didn’t tell you guys.

27
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,824
What are you saying?

28
00:04:16,450 --> 00:04:21,913
The truth is...

29
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,501
we’re back together.

30
00:04:28,012 --> 00:04:35,772
But it was only after we found out the DNA test results were fake.

31
00:04:50,300 --> 00:04:51,236
WHAT?!

32
00:04:52,812 --> 00:04:54,810
But don't you dare tell anyone.

33
00:04:55,710 --> 00:04:57,760
I'm telling you this because I trust you.

34
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:03,876
Why didn’t you tell me from the start?

35
00:05:04,540 --> 00:05:08,135
If anyone else had heard what you two were doing in the restroom,

36
00:05:08,153 --> 00:05:09,673
what do you think they’d be saying right now?

37
00:05:11,298 --> 00:05:13,290
Thank you for warning us.

38
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:19,003
Oh, That hurts.

39
00:05:19,210 --> 00:05:19,907
You deserve it!

40
00:05:20,460 --> 00:05:24,080
I told you not to mess around at the office, didn't I?

41
00:05:25,452 --> 00:05:27,015
But you’re just so cute, Ran.

42
00:05:31,181 --> 00:05:32,818
What a relief.

43
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,676
I was worried that I couldn’t look at you two faces.

44
00:05:39,550 --> 00:05:42,855
So, that means Auntie Jintana has been lying to everyone this whole time?

45
00:05:46,850 --> 00:05:50,326
I... I’m really sorry on my mother's behalf.

46
00:05:53,980 --> 00:05:55,766
It’s not your fault, Ran.

47
00:05:57,544 --> 00:05:58,307
Thank you.

48
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:03,335
Alright then! So, what are you guys gonna do next?

49
00:06:04,730 --> 00:06:06,030
That’s exactly what I was about to say.

50
00:06:07,590 --> 00:06:09,126
Ran and I have already thought it over.

51
00:06:10,150 --> 00:06:11,680
I have something I need you guys to help us with.

52
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:15,280
We’re going to set a trap to double-cross Jintana.

53
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,243
The thing is...

54
00:06:18,850 --> 00:06:21,224
we want to talk to Mom first.

55
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:25,913
We want her to step down from her position willingly.

56
00:06:27,341 --> 00:06:29,340
If she leaves quietly,

57
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:32,166
she won’t have to go to prison

58
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,590
especially since P’Chat has already agreed to it.

59
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:41,809
And what about you?

60
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:42,769
Huh...

61
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:44,129
"Nu"?

62
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,510
You mean her?

63
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:50,996
Her neck..

64
00:06:53,450 --> 00:06:55,304
No. I didn’t see.

65
00:06:55,730 --> 00:06:56,750
Why?

66
00:06:57,770 --> 00:06:58,892
I see you guys fighting all the time.

67
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:00,369
How did you guys end up like this?

68
00:07:01,193 --> 00:07:03,190
Did you just call her... "Nu"?

69
00:07:03,581 --> 00:07:04,849
Don't even start.

70
00:07:06,123 --> 00:07:08,120
It’s not like I asked her to call me that.

71
00:07:08,633 --> 00:07:09,138
Whoa..

72
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:11,181
What are you gonna do?

73
00:07:11,950 --> 00:07:13,366
If you don't help me, I'll expose you.

74
00:07:14,910 --> 00:07:15,864
Whatever.

75
00:07:17,210 --> 00:07:17,993
I'm in. I'll help.

76
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:21,218
Thank you.

77
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:27,113
One week later

78
00:07:29,400 --> 00:07:30,689
Here is your coffee.

79
00:07:37,590 --> 00:07:38,443
Pimchat.

80
00:07:40,930 --> 00:07:42,369
Hmm... What's wrong?

81
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,824
Someone might see us like this.

82
00:07:47,050 --> 00:07:49,495
I heard the door lock.

83
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:55,532
Well... it’s better to be safe.

84
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:59,532
You’re even naughtier than I am.

85
00:08:10,270 --> 00:08:13,452
In that case, before I drink this coffee...

86
00:08:14,750 --> 00:08:17,704
Can I get a little "sugar" first?

87
00:08:56,060 --> 00:08:57,095
Yes Mom.

88
00:09:01,450 --> 00:09:02,658
Right now?

89
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,464
Okay,

90
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,710
I don't have anything else going on.

91
00:09:11,710 --> 00:09:12,800
I’ll be there.

92
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:17,470
What’s wrong?

93
00:09:21,330 --> 00:09:22,910
My mother wants me to go see her.

94
00:09:25,340 --> 00:09:26,904
And you’re actually going?

95
00:09:29,450 --> 00:09:30,738
I have to.

96
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,732
Now that you’ve met Ranya,

97
00:09:54,769 --> 00:09:56,215
what do you think, Mr. Kim?

98
00:09:57,610 --> 00:09:58,640
She’s beautiful.

99
00:09:59,780 --> 00:10:02,689
I think we’ll get along quite well.

100
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:08,424
Ranya is a very good girl.

101
00:10:08,850 --> 00:10:11,501
She’s polite, well-mannered, and sweet.

102
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,113
That’s great to hear.

103
00:10:15,230 --> 00:10:17,612
Um, excuse me...

104
00:10:18,390 --> 00:10:20,664
what are you talking about?

105
00:10:23,710 --> 00:10:26,203
This is Mr. Kimhant,

106
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:28,301
the Chairman of Holder Group.

107
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:31,181
I want you two to get to know each other

108
00:10:31,723 --> 00:10:33,720
since you’re going to be getting engaged, after all.

109
00:10:34,470 --> 00:10:35,040
Wait...

110
00:10:36,110 --> 00:10:36,978
what?!
